WEBVTT

1
00:06:19.410 --> 00:06:20.700 
我为你效力
I worked for you.

2
00:06:22.070 --> 00:06:23.840 
听好  你输了
Listen, you lost.

3
00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:25.020 
但还有一多半国民
But more than half the country

4
00:06:25.020 --> 00:06:27.220 
仍然认为你是他们的总统
still considers you their president.

5
00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:28.600 
你必须要面对他们
This is what's required.

6
00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:30.300 
走出去  发表讲话
Go down there, give your speech.

7
00:06:33.420 --> 00:06:34.550 
认输吧
Concede.

